flowchart LR
    WH[Webhook Delivery]

    WH --> SIGN[sign: HMAC-SHA256\nX-AXME-Signature header]
    SIGN --> SEND[POST to webhook_url]
    SEND --> TARGET[Target Service]
    TARGET --> EXTRACT[extract header signature]
    TARGET --> REBUILD[rebuild expected signature\nshared secret + raw body]
    EXTRACT & REBUILD --> COMPARE{match?}
    COMPARE -->|yes| ACCEPT[process event]
    COMPARE -->|no| REJECT[reject 403 / log]
    ACCEPT --> ACK[200 OK → marks DELIVERED]
    REJECT --> RETRY[AXME retries with backoff]
